name: Ten (10) Ketchup Packets of Unknown Age and Provenance
description: This NFT represents the underlying asset pictured in the attached photograph: ten ketchup packets. Nine of the ketchup packets purportedly contain Heinz ketchup, and the remaining packet is labeled "Chef's Quality". If you would like to exercise this NFT to redeem it for the underlying asset, please burn it after your purchase, then Tweet the address of the burn transaction to @BenRegenspan to arrange for shipment to a mainland US shipping address.
